# RE-PROOF on astrid 0.9.4 (captured 2026-07-12, UTC) — latest released kernel
#
# Published JS SDK 0.1.0 components stopped installing on kernels >= 0.9.1
# ("component imports instance `astrid:process/host@1.0.0`, but a matching
# implementation was not found in the linker"). Fixed locally by dropping the
# unused astrid:process import from the synthesized world + SDK bridge (see
# patch-sdk.mjs section 3 and patches/UPSTREAM.md) — component shrank from
# 13.10 MB / 170 host imports to 12.30 MB / 142.
